# Processed Positions
# GET /processed-positions
# Returns logged positions that were processed (move calculations and game analyses).
# Requires MySQL to be configured (MYSQL_DATABASE_URI).

### All processed positions (no filter)
GET {{HEX_AI_DISTRIBUTED_API}}/processed-positions

### Positions in a date range
GET {{HEX_AI_DISTRIBUTED_API}}/processed-positions?createdAfter=2024-09-04T00:00:00.000Z&createdBefore=2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z

### Positions since a specific date
GET {{HEX_AI_DISTRIBUTED_API}}/processed-positions?createdAfter=2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z
